jqkAjjYJ2nQ">Thứ vận Trần thượng thư đề Nguyễn bố chánh thảo đường - 次韻陳尚書題阮布政草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-%C3%8Dch-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-m%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%C6%A1n-hoa-t%C3%A1c-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-xvuCjjK6llPv3YKSrMLDfw">Thưởng mẫu đơn hoa, tác thủ kệ tử - 賞牡丹花,作首偈子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-%C3%8Dch-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-GDbpL33fyMju5deb5LyeVg">Văn Ích thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/T%E1%BB%91ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Duy%E1%BB%87t-chi-H%E1%BA%A5p-Ch%C3%A2u-y%E1%BA%BFt-Ti%E1%BA%BFt-th%E1%BB%8B-lang/poem-a2y_wd0HDdapVB9hdqFrkg">Tống Trịnh Duyệt chi Hấp Châu yết Tiết thị lang - 送鄭說之歙州謁薛侍郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-ge9IfP4qAzGhQhdEqnXX9g">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-GrfZ83486gEgzshT4ctASA">Đoàn Nguyễn Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Xuy-ti%C3%AAu-%E1%BB%B7/poem-h32S3FNQSPCV3lcay75INQ">Xuy tiêu ỷ - 吹簫倚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
